title: Cannot invoke method toBytes() on null object
body:
Error caused when executing your workflow.

`Cannot invoke method toBytes() on null object`

The error appears to be on `line 73` for memory parameter.

title: Use global fragment length specified in cli options when not shifting
Running Zerone on merged bams is not working
Zerone process does not work when using the same input for two replicates
SPP model process is hanging with Singularity
body: `run_spp.R` uses the the [snow](https://github.com/cran/snow) library to create clusters of nodes if `-p` is specified. This does not work within a Singularity container.
